# {{lb|zh|literary}} [[only]] [[then]]; not ... [[until]]
#: {{syn|zh|才}}
#* {{zh-x|^趙 王 送 璧 時 齋戒 五 日。今 大王 亦 宜 齋戒 五日，設 九賓 於 廷，臣 乃 敢 上 璧。|The King of Zhao fasted for five days before sending the jade off. Now Your Majesty should also fast for five days, and receive me with the Ceremony of Jiubin at the court. Only then will I dare to present the jade.|ref=Shiji}}
#* {{zh-x|^沛 ^公 謂 ^張 ^良 曰：「從 此 道 至 吾 軍，不過 二十 里 耳。度{duò} 我 至 軍 中，公 乃 入。」|Liu Bang said to Zhang Liang, "It is only twenty ''li''s from here to our camp. '''Only after''' you estimate that I have arrived at our camp should you enter."|ref=Shiji}}
# {{lb|zh|literary}} [[but]]
#* {{zh-x|不 見 ^子-都，乃 見 狂且。|I do not see Zidu, '''but''' I see this mad fellow.|ref=Shijing}}
#* {{quote-song|zh|year=11th c.|author=lw:zh:司馬光<t:{{w|Sima Guang}}>|title=s:zh:訓儉示康}}
#*: {{zh-q|古人 以 儉 為{wéi} 美德，今人 乃 以 儉 相{xiāng} 詬病。|The ancient people regarded frugality as a virtue, '''but''' now people criticize one another for being frugal.|CL}}
# {{lb|zh|literary}} [[surprisingly]]; [[unexpectedly]]
#: {{syn|zh|竟然}}
#* {{quote-song|zh|trans-title=[[s:Tao hua yuan ji|The Peach Blossom Spring]]|title=lw:zh:桃花源記|author=lw:zh:陶淵明<t:{{w|Tao Yuanming}}>|year=421}}
#*: {{zh-q|問 今 是 何 世，乃 不知 有 漢，無論 ^魏 ^晉。|They asked what the current ruling dynasty was. '''Surprisingly''', they had not even heard of the Han, let alone the Wei and the Jin. <small>[Wiktionary translation]</small>|CL}}
